My only tip is to stay away from cyanoacrylics. I used superglue to try to
attach a motor to a brick, and it started eating away the brick. Stuck like a
champ, but I had red "puss" all over the place.

Max Davies wrote:

> I have found a simple way to attach non-Lego motors to Lego components.
